        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Extracurricular x 4Aces Apparel Collection, Now Available on TRENDYGOLF",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>LIV Golf is changing the game, bringing an exciting, fast-paced format that's attracting new fans and redefining what it means to be part of the golf community. The LIV Tour Team Championship, set to take place at Maridoe Golf Club in Dallas from September 20-22, is the ultimate celebration of this bold new era in golf. And as always, the 4Aces Golf Club will be leading the charge—not just with their performance, but with their style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
