    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Extracurricular x 4Aces apparel collection, now available on TRENDYGOLF, captures the spirit of this movement. This special edition collection, designed in collaboration with the 4Aces—Dustin Johnson, Patrick Reed, Pat Perez, and Harold Varner III—combines the performance demands of golf apparel with a modern, fashion-forward aesthetic.</p><p>LIV Golf has brought an element of fun and inclusivity to the game, making it more accessible and dynamic for fans and players alike. The 4Aces epitomize this vibe, balancing competition with camaraderie, all while setting a new standard for how the game should look and feel. The Extracurricular x 4Aces collection is a reflection of that ethos. With polos, hoodies, tees, and hats designed for ultimate versatility, these pieces aren't just for the course—they're for wherever life takes you. Whether you're teeing off, hanging out with friends, or hitting the town, this collection delivers style and performance in equal measure.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_1"
