    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Crafted with premium fabrics and standout designs, this gear not only looks good, it works just as hard as the 4Aces on tour. Expect comfortable, breathable materials that move with you, keeping you cool and confident in any situation. And with the 4Aces logo front and center, you'll be representing the best-dressed team in golf, a team that's making waves both on the leaderboard and in the fashion world.</p><p><strong>Why this collection matters: </strong>LIV Golf is shaking up a sport that's been long overdue for a refresh. It's no longer just about tradition—it's about pushing the boundaries, embracing boldness, and making golf fun again. The Extracurricular x 4Aces collection embodies this new attitude, offering a modern twist on classic golf wear. For fans of the 4Aces and LIV Golf's electric atmosphere, this collection is more than just apparel—it's a celebration of a sport that's evolving.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
