            "text": "<p></p><ul><li>What: Special collection of Extracurricular x 4Aces apparel</li><li>Where: LIV Tour Team Championship, Maridoe Golf Club, Dallas, Texas</li><li>When: September 20–22</li><li>Who: 4Aces Golf Club featuring Dustin Johnson, Patrick Reed, Pat Perez, and Harold Varner III</li><li>Why: Celebrating the best-dressed team in golf</li></ul><p>Don't miss the chance to shop the collection and support the 4Aces as they bring both their skills and their style to Dallas.</p>"
